Text: Please. someone, please seed season 7 episodes. I've been searching for 3 days now. I need to watch!
There is no Season 7 and I think if there will be one, another person will be the tracker.
There is a season 7 and the first episode aired last week. There is a new tracker and his name is Chad Savage. There is also a documentary that preceeded the season called "Searching for Mantracker"
Well, I wish some Canadian would start reliably capturing episodes then!
